---
title: Homestyle Meatloaf with Roasted Sweet Potato and Cheesy Broccoli
description: Meatloaf is a classic dish that gets a tasty update in this recipe. This meatloaf is made tender with breadcrumbs and made sweet with a BBQ sauce glaze. Paired with sweet potato wedges and cheesy broccoli you won't be able to decide which part of this meal you like best!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/homestyle-meatloaf-d1d5ee82.jpg
